descriptionHTML:
The WearSeek App searches for pictures on the Internet using the keywords you provide and displays them in sequence on your Android Wear device.

To use the application follow these steps:
1. Open the application on your mobile device and provide some keywords.
2. Open the application on your Wear product and select a keyword.

After you've finished step 1, you can close the application on the mobile device. The wear the application works even if the phone is closed.

After step 2, the application will display a picture every 5 seconds.

The application was tested with Nexus S and Samsung Gear.

Keywords: wearseek, wear, Internet, image search, web, picture, image, search, display,
